title: [Grawood Farmstead, Town]
description: Storefronts and houses line the street's edge, their porches and railings decorated with flowered wreaths and colorful ribbons.  Banners hang in sweeping scallops from a roof's edge here and there, and multihued lanterns hang from tall wooden posts, casting a spray of colored light across the ground as small candles flicker within.
